who had claimed zias decree was unconstitutional and would 
unfairly favor governing party candidates 
pakistan today has a real chance of moving towards national 
unity ms bhutto said in a telephone interview from her 
residence in the southern port of karachi where she is resting 
following the birth of her first child sept 21 
representative government will be set up which would work 
for the peace and stability of the country ms bhutto said 
