the heavens with awe and wonder since the dawn of human existence 
we can comprehend why our countrymen have been driven to explore 
the vast expanse of space and we are convinced that this is the 
road to the future the road that americans must travel if we are 
to maintain the dream of our constitution to secure the blessings 
of liberty to ourselves and our posterity 
richard o covey 
as we the crew of discovery witness this earthly splendor from 
