economy is concerned on the side of the hardliners led by musavi 
who insist on tight state control of the economy and extreme 
suspicion toward foreign involvement 
but it also underlined the political uncertainty that has 
gripped iran since its sudden acceptance of a united 
nationssponsored ceasefire that took effect aug20 
