<TEXT>
the talk of lisbon these days is about 
the chiado the 10block area of 19thcentury department stores and 
shops swept by fire aug 25 
most of the talk centers on the chiados future in the heart of 
the city 
will it be restored to what it was will modern highrises win 
out 
i think they will have to preserve the facades of the district 
