exporter issued a sharply worded statement late in the day saying 
that while it believes returning to prescribed production levels 
is the best way for restoring full stability to world oil 
markets it will not freeze its own production while others 
continue to violate their ceilings 
crude oil settled 28 cents to 31 cents lower with november at 
