sides reached an impasse last spring many attendants refused to 
work overtime on the memorial day weekend forcing usair to cancel 
some 170 flights then 
the union and the company now must go through the same process 
to integrate a contract covering some 3000 flight attendants at 
piedmont airlines into the usair accord 
usair purchased piedmont last november 
